message: "If you use this software, please cite it as below."
type: software
title: "Resource-Efficient LLMs for Depression Symptoms Screening: Performance and Limitations in Zero-Shot Setting"
abstract: >
  Zero-shot classification of DSM-5 Major Depressive Disorder symptom categories
  from text using multiple open-source large language models. Includes a flexible
  multi-architecture LLM classification pipeline and a Kaggle-compatible analysis
  notebook for evaluation of model performance and misclassification patterns.
